Package org.ejbca.core.protocol.cmp

Class NestedMessageContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ejbca.core.protocol.cmp.BaseCmpMessage
      • org.ejbca.core.protocol.cmp.NestedMessageContent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, RequestMessage
    public class NestedMessageContent
extends BaseCmpMessage
implements RequestMessage
    Nested Message Content according to RFC4210. The PKI message is signed by an RA authority. The PKIMessage body is another PKIMessage containing the request to be processed.
    Version:
    $Id: NestedMessageContent.java 28096 2018-01-25 05:34:38Z andresjakobs $

        Get the key from a certification request.
        Specified by:
        getRequestPublicKey in interface RequestMessage

        InvalidKeyException - If the key is invalid.
